{"tid":2099599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屋宇署疑禁公眾查閱國安公署新址圖則 本研社：土地資訊也變「國家機密」 研究隨時踩紅線","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T10:38:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3154abcbf502d602e26c966fd3d156ff6deef722","tid":2099599,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"中央駐港維護國家安全公署於銅鑼灣維景酒店的臨時辦公室，今日（8 日）清晨開幕；「本土研究社」發現，屋宇署查閱樓宇及小型工程的記錄系統「百樓圖網」（BRAVO），搜尋不到銅鑼灣維景酒店的圖則，不過在灣仔、旺角和的何文田的維景酒店，仍能找到圖則。本研社質疑當局刪除公開資訊，連土地資訊也變成「國家機密」，在開放資訊方面「開倒車」，擔心日後資訊空間日益收窄，連研究都隨時踩中「紅線」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B1%8B%E5%AE%87%E7%BD%B2%E7%96%91%E7%A6%81%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E6%96%B0%E5%9D%80%E5%9C%96%E5%89%87-%E6%9C%AC%E7%A0%94%E7%A4%BE-%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E4%B9%9F%E8%AE%8A-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E8%B8%A9%E7%B4%85%E7%B7%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25AE%2587%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2596%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259D%2580%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2589%2587-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25A8%258A%25E4%25B9%259F%25E8%25AE%258A-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25B7%259A%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK2%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=21eb7ff6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25AE%2587%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2596%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5